text: "What If" is a 2010 song by Jason Derulo and is the fourth single from his self-titled debut studio album. It went to number 8 in Belgium, number 12 in the United Kingdom, number 16 in Ireland, number 27 in New Zealand, number 32 in Australia, number 35 in Austria, number 48 in Germany and number 76 in the United States. == Track listings == * CD single and digital download # "What If" – 3:22 # "What If" (Wideboys radio edit) – 3:20 * UK iTunes EP # "What If" (album version) – 3:22 # "What If" (Wideboys radio edit) – 3:20 # "What If" (Wideboys club mix 5) – 5:50 # "What If" (Electric Allstars mix) – 3:20 # "What If" (music video) – 4:15 == References == Category:2010 songs Category:Jason Derulo songs
title: What If (Jason Derulo song)
